## 8. Edge Cases

### 8.1 Configuration Override

**Scenario**: User provides custom baseUrl via config

```typescript
const service = new AviDMService({
  baseUrl: 'https://production-api.example.com'
});
```

**Expected**: Custom URL used instead of default
**Test**: Unit test verifies override works

### 8.2 Port Already in Use

**Scenario**: Port 3001 occupied by another process

**Expected**: Backend fails to start (detected by health check)
**Fallback**: AviDMService offline mode activates (if enabled)

### 8.3 CORS Issues

**Scenario**: Backend CORS whitelist doesn't include frontend origin

**Current Whitelist**:
```javascript
const corsWhitelist = [
  'http://localhost:5173', // ✅ Frontend dev server
  'http://localhost:3000',
  'http://localhost:3001'
];
```

**Expected**: No CORS issues (5173 whitelisted)
**Validation**: Integration tests verify CORS headers

